snippet.title: DCS MB-339 | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Our third party developer IndiaFoxtEcho is proud to announce that DCS: MB-339 is available from our eShop and from Steam. This exceptionally capable aircraft is really worth a look. Check out the details of this remarkable trainer, light attack, and aerobatic aircraft and enjoy!

DCS eShop: https://www.digitalcombatsimulator.com/en/shop/modules/mb-339/
DCS on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/223750/DCS_World_Steam_Edition/

☑ Site: http://digitalcombatsimulator.com/
